Mong.ui - MongoDB Gui built on python


FEATURES

- Tabbed interface



INSTALLATION:

- Depends on wxPython 2.8+ and pymongo



CREDITS:

- Development by Vinicius Lima (eu@viniciuslima.com)
- Logo and icon artwork by Alexandre Sakai




